WEBVTT

00:01:07.439 --> 00:01:07.959
Zhao Qihai

00:01:12.599 --> 00:01:13.400
What's going on?

00:01:13.799 --> 00:01:14.280
Zhao Qihai

00:01:18.519 --> 00:01:19.519
What... what happened to him?

00:01:21.280 --> 00:01:21.640
Zhao Qihai

00:01:22.319 --> 00:01:22.680
Zhao Qihai

00:01:26.159 --> 00:01:27.040
He's not dead, is he?

00:01:28.159 --> 00:01:28.599
Di Fu

00:01:29.359 --> 00:01:29.840
Where is she hiding?

00:01:30.439 --> 00:01:31.159
I just saw her.

00:01:32.079 --> 00:01:32.439
Di Fu

00:01:33.079 --> 00:01:34.079
I saw Di Fu just now.

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:35.040
She wants to kill me.

00:01:36.519 --> 00:01:37.040
Zhao Qihai

00:01:37.359 --> 00:01:37.840
Zhao Qihai

00:01:40.959 --> 00:01:41.760
What did Di Fu say to you?

00:01:41.760 --> 00:01:42.439
She wants to kill me.

00:02:08.919 --> 00:02:10.000
Zhao Qihai

00:02:13.879 --> 00:02:15.080
You raped me.

00:02:15.599 --> 00:02:16.800
I'm going to kill you.

00:02:17.159 --> 00:02:17.719
No.

00:02:18.080 --> 00:02:19.199
She didn't say anything.

00:02:19.439 --> 00:02:20.199
She said nothing.

00:02:20.520 --> 00:02:20.919
She didn't say.

00:02:21.240 --> 00:02:22.280
Please, take me away.

00:02:22.280 --> 00:02:23.680
Don't leave me here alone.

00:02:25.039 --> 00:02:27.560
Hurry, take me away!

00:02:27.560 --> 00:02:28.360
Come on, give me a hand.

00:02:29.080 --> 00:02:29.360
Come on.

00:02:50.759 --> 00:02:51.479
Don't come over.

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:54.479
Fang Qiu

00:02:55.199 --> 00:02:56.919
As soon as I pull this knife out,

00:02:57.199 --> 00:02:58.599
you're dead.

00:02:58.840 --> 00:02:59.719
Tell me now.

00:03:00.360 --> 00:03:01.879
Where exactly is my daughter?

00:03:01.960 --> 00:03:02.879
Is she dead or alive?

00:03:02.879 --> 00:03:04.840
I... I really don't know.

00:03:05.120 --> 00:03:07.120
I really don't know.

00:03:07.479 --> 00:03:09.000
Then go to hell.

00:03:18.919 --> 00:03:20.319
It's a good thing you were here.

00:03:20.520 --> 00:03:22.199
Otherwise, who knows how many would have died.

00:03:24.400 --> 00:03:25.199
The DNA of the burnt female corpse...

00:03:25.199 --> 00:03:26.120
is the report out?

00:03:26.400 --> 00:03:27.520
It's out. It's at the station.

00:03:28.840 --> 00:03:29.400
Go back and get Ma Shan

00:03:29.400 --> 00:03:30.319
to do a DNA collection too.

00:03:39.520 --> 00:03:40.560
Take the female corpse's DNA and Ma Shan's

00:03:40.560 --> 00:03:41.360
and run a comparison.

00:03:41.520 --> 00:03:42.360
Tell me when it's done.

00:03:43.080 --> 00:03:43.560
Okay.

00:03:45.439 --> 00:03:45.840
Okay.

00:03:46.319 --> 00:03:47.039
Inspector Qi

00:03:49.520 --> 00:03:51.000
What happened these past two days

00:03:51.560 --> 00:03:52.719
feels just like a dream.

00:03:53.039 --> 00:03:54.400
Too much has happened these past two days.

00:03:55.080 --> 00:03:56.879
But there are also many unsolved mysteries.

00:03:58.319 --> 00:03:59.599
Inspector Qi, thank you for your hard work.

00:04:00.639 --> 00:04:01.319
Tonight,

00:04:01.599 --> 00:04:02.639
you can finally get some rest.

00:04:03.159 --> 00:04:04.360
I can't rest yet.

00:04:05.439 --> 00:04:06.800
Come back with me later to give a statement.

00:04:12.319 --> 00:04:12.919
Lawyer Luo

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:13.759
You two.

00:04:13.759 --> 00:04:14.520
I am very sorry.

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:15.319
The heavy rain blocked the road.

00:04:15.319 --> 00:04:16.279
I really couldn't get in.

00:04:18.879 --> 00:04:19.800
What exactly happened?

00:04:20.680 --> 00:04:21.279
Where are the others?

00:04:22.319 --> 00:04:24.439
Zhao Qihai and Fang Qiu were injured

00:04:24.639 --> 00:04:25.639
and taken away by ambulance.

00:04:26.639 --> 00:04:27.360
Ma Shan

00:04:27.879 --> 00:04:28.920
was arrested for the attack.

00:04:32.720 --> 00:04:33.839
Under the current circumstances,

00:04:34.920 --> 00:04:36.600
I'll announce the will a bit later.

00:04:36.600 --> 00:04:37.560
Lawyer Luo

00:04:38.959 --> 00:04:41.079
Let's wait for the police investigation results before announcing it.

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:52.759
Come upstairs with me to take a look.

00:05:05.360 --> 00:05:07.519
After we heard Zhao Qihai shouting,

00:05:07.519 --> 00:05:08.639
we broke down the door to get in.

00:05:09.480 --> 00:05:10.439
But I remember

00:05:10.800 --> 00:05:12.240
when we left his room,

00:05:12.759 --> 00:05:13.959
the room wasn't locked.

00:05:15.199 --> 00:05:16.000
That's right.

00:05:17.680 --> 00:05:19.360
Zhao Qihai was unconscious at the time.

00:05:20.759 --> 00:05:22.480
But who locked the door from the inside?

00:05:23.040 --> 00:05:23.920
That's one thing.

00:05:25.279 --> 00:05:25.920
Secondly,

00:05:27.839 --> 00:05:28.360
Ma Shan...

00:05:29.360 --> 00:05:30.279
Ma Shan...

00:05:32.079 --> 00:05:33.959
she appeared and stabbed Fang Qiu,

00:05:34.839 --> 00:05:37.040
but her hand was handcuffed to the headboard.

00:05:43.319 --> 00:05:44.720
I went to Ma Shan's room.

00:05:46.240 --> 00:05:48.000
Not only were the handcuffs unlocked,

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:51.399
even the handcuffs were gone.

00:06:01.279 --> 00:06:02.680
Ma Shan's room

00:06:04.959 --> 00:06:07.120
is directly above Zhao Qihai's room.

00:06:39.920 --> 00:06:41.079
Where to, Chief?

00:06:41.199 --> 00:06:42.279
Go check the villa again.

00:06:42.720 --> 00:06:43.759
How did the questioning of Ma Shan go?

00:06:45.240 --> 00:06:46.279
That's basically it.

00:06:46.639 --> 00:06:48.360
I'm thinking about searching her home.

00:06:49.600 --> 00:06:50.800
How are Fang Qiu and Zhao Qihai?

00:06:51.319 --> 00:06:52.079
Fang Qiu hasn't woken up yet.

00:06:52.279 --> 00:06:53.600
Zhao Qihai refuses to say anything.

00:06:54.120 --> 00:06:55.040
He's demanding to see a lawyer.

00:06:56.560 --> 00:06:57.240
A lawyer.

00:06:59.160 --> 00:06:59.800
Not surprising.

00:07:00.600 --> 00:07:01.160
Keep a close eye on him.

00:07:01.480 --> 00:07:01.759
Okay.

00:07:02.079 --> 00:07:02.439
Don't worry.

00:07:08.680 --> 00:07:10.000
The content of the will hasn't been released yet.

00:07:10.519 --> 00:07:12.160
Can we find a way, through legal channels,

00:07:12.879 --> 00:07:13.600
to get a copy?

00:07:14.240 --> 00:07:15.360
I'll figure something out.

00:07:16.879 --> 00:07:18.040
The DNA of the female corpse and Ma Shan...

00:07:18.040 --> 00:07:19.000
Is the comparison result out yet?

00:07:19.439 --> 00:07:20.800
It's a bit tricky.

00:07:21.920 --> 00:07:24.399
Do you suspect that female corpse is Lin Niannian?

00:07:27.519 --> 00:07:28.040
Where is Chen Ting?

00:07:28.600 --> 00:07:30.480
He went to check Li Ran's old house early this morning.

00:07:32.319 --> 00:07:33.240
Whether it's the content of the will,

00:07:33.240 --> 00:07:34.480
or the DNA report,

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:35.279
as soon as there are results,

00:07:35.279 --> 00:07:35.959
notify me immediately.

00:07:35.959 --> 00:07:36.759
Don't delay for a second.

00:07:37.199 --> 00:07:37.480
Yes, sir.

00:07:42.920 --> 00:07:43.439
Inspector Qi.

00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:45.079
The area around the Li family's old house

00:07:45.240 --> 00:07:46.160
is an urban village.

00:07:47.519 --> 00:07:48.959
The government proposed redevelopment a few years ago.

00:07:49.160 --> 00:07:50.040
Many people have moved away.

00:07:51.560 --> 00:07:52.680
It's pretty desolate now.

00:07:52.959 --> 00:07:53.680
Hardly anyone lives here.

00:07:54.920 --> 00:07:55.639
I'm just afraid

00:07:57.439 --> 00:07:58.439
we won't find anything.

00:07:59.600 --> 00:08:00.759
Have you talked to Li Ran's foster parents?

00:08:01.800 --> 00:08:02.560
I tried to schedule a meeting several times.

00:08:02.560 --> 00:08:03.480
They said they didn't have time.

00:08:04.160 --> 00:08:04.680
Figure something out.

00:08:05.639 --> 00:08:06.920
I plan to go straight to their house later

00:08:06.920 --> 00:08:07.519
and knock on their door.

00:08:08.439 --> 00:08:09.920
See if I can get a word with them.

00:08:10.279 --> 00:08:10.639
Alright.

00:08:11.319 --> 00:08:11.839
Waiting for your news.

00:08:13.240 --> 00:08:13.519
Sir.

00:08:14.399 --> 00:08:15.040
About ten years ago,

00:08:15.040 --> 00:08:16.279
did a pair of sisters live here?

00:08:18.680 --> 00:08:19.319
Inspector Qi.

00:08:19.720 --> 00:08:20.480
What brings you here?

00:08:21.000 --> 00:08:21.439
Please come in.

00:08:22.519 --> 00:08:23.199
I just came to look around.

00:08:23.920 --> 00:08:25.240
To see if anything was missed.

00:08:26.519 --> 00:08:27.199
Inspector Qi.

00:08:27.759 --> 00:08:28.399
Thank you.

00:08:28.959 --> 00:08:31.040
I know you must have helped behind the scenes.

00:08:31.360 --> 00:08:31.959
Otherwise, I wouldn't be able to

00:08:31.959 --> 00:08:32.919
stay here all this time.

00:08:34.200 --> 00:08:34.639
A Si.

00:08:36.919 --> 00:08:38.279
Why do you insist on staying here?

00:08:39.799 --> 00:08:41.559
Before the Master and Madam passed away,

00:08:41.960 --> 00:08:42.960
I promised them.

00:08:43.679 --> 00:08:45.159
Until the will is announced,

00:08:45.399 --> 00:08:46.320
I will not leave.

00:08:47.480 --> 00:08:49.480
They aren't leaving this villa to you, are they?

00:08:50.159 --> 00:08:51.120
You're joking.

00:08:51.399 --> 00:08:52.440
I wouldn't dare hope for that.

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:53.759
Let's go inside and sit.

00:08:55.720 --> 00:08:57.159
So many things happened in here.

00:08:58.279 --> 00:08:58.960
Aren't you afraid?

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:01.840
Everyone has to go someday.

00:09:02.720 --> 00:09:03.480
Besides,

00:09:03.919 --> 00:09:05.120
the Master and Madam

00:09:05.120 --> 00:09:06.799
were always very good to me when they were alive.

00:09:08.759 --> 00:09:08.960
By the way.

00:09:08.960 --> 00:09:11.639
What exactly happened between Zhao Qihai and Di Fu?

00:09:12.399 --> 00:09:13.360
The dead should be respected.

00:09:13.759 --> 00:09:14.399
I...

00:09:14.799 --> 00:09:16.639
don't want to cause any more trouble for the Madam.

00:09:17.200 --> 00:09:17.639
I'm sorry.

00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:20.840
Fair enough.

00:09:22.559 --> 00:09:23.360
People...

00:09:23.399 --> 00:09:24.480
the more they can't have something,

00:09:25.279 --> 00:09:26.519
the greater the hatred in their hearts.

00:09:27.399 --> 00:09:29.440
Zhao Qihai was always verbally abusive towards Di Fu.

00:09:31.399 --> 00:09:32.039
I wonder...

00:09:32.840 --> 00:09:34.480
did he really want to possess his sister-in-law?

00:09:37.720 --> 00:09:38.919
Can I use the restroom?

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:43.960
He gets whatever he wants.

00:09:48.480 --> 00:09:50.240
He just uses forceful means.